sentences: Whitney Chitwood is a stand-up comedian from Chicago.
Her debut album, 2019's The Bakery Case, was produced by Grammy winner Dan Schlissel for Stand Up!
She performed in her first show at six months old.
She has performed with Eddie Pepitone, Adam Conover, and River Butcher.
It was recorded live at the Green Mill.
A reviewer for comedy website The Interrobang praised the album, saying that with "her chronic chainsmoker voice and a jawline that could take down an oak tree ...
"She appeared in a 2019 episode of the NBC TV series  Chicago P.D. She hosts the podcast Is This Us?
